items.description: One of the tourist places in Guwahati, Nehru Park is perfect for families. The lush greenery of the park is refreshing and will ensure a good time during your visit. The kids will love this place as they would get to ride different swings. The highlight inside the park are the concrete sculptures depicting various dances such as Ojapali, Deodhani, Bihu and Bor Taal. Other than that, you also have an open-air theatre wherein you may get to witness performances by local artists if you time it right. This is one of the most beautiful places to visit in Guwahati for couples.

items.name: The Serene Arc
items.section_excerpt: Another best among the places to see in Guwahati is the suburban town of Pandu. The place is named after King Pandu, who was the father of the Pandavas. There is a temple dedicated to Pandu, called the Pandunath Temple here at Tila Hills. It is believed that the Pandavas stayed here during their exile. Do plan a visit to this serene place to encounter the astounding beauty of Guwahati.
